  <name>Minesweeper</name>
  <summary>Classic Windows Minesweeper game</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      The classic Minesweeper game from Windows, running through Wine.
      Clear the board of mines by flagging them and revealing safe squares.
    </p>
    <p>
      This Flatpak demonstrates how to package old Windows games using the
      Wine extension system, with optional gamescope integration for HiDPI
      scaling.
    </p>
    <p>
      Features:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Classic Minesweeper gameplay</li>
      <li>Runs through Wine 10.x extension</li>
      <li>Optional gamescope integration for scaling</li>
      <li>Persistent game settings</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

  <launchable type="desktop-id">io.github.jokujossai.wine.minesweeper.desktop</launchable>

  <url type="homepage">https://github.com/jokujossai/wine-flatpak</url>
